l damages&nbsp;related to the Group&rsquo;s failure to utilize its room block.</p>\\n"}','[]','0','0',0,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'["ZHSP","ZMGR","ZMNI","ZHBP","ZHIM","ZMSU","ZHLB","ZRPL","ZRCZ","ZCJG","ZPLB","CDS"]',1,'2019-08-01 17:07:36.000','dareyes','','2019-08-01 17:07:36.000')
